name: consumed by pixels
description:
Digitally consumed by pixels.

Originally a photograph I took of my friend in Walsall Art Gallery on the 6th August 2006. Back then I used old-school photosuite vista software that came with a Vivitar camera at the time. The creation was part of my 'Flashcore x photography'. A collection of art & photography I made at age 15 but never shared. Today, 24/05/21 I've recovered it from a CD to finally get seen and re-edited it using Photoshop to be more current.
